law.catch_line: Plans must comply with department's rules and regulations.
law.text: All plans authorized by this chapter shall conform to all rules and regulations promulgated by the Department of Public Advocacy.
law.history: Repealed, reenacted, renumbered, and amended 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 283, sec. 9, effective July 15, 2002. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 33, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 358, sec. 7.
